{
  "stem": "9995.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Smha Scpera, may he burn in hell, he completely identified himself with the German.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before the war, he was a clerk in the [HEBREW], namely the Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember he was coming to our house to collect the dues from grandfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And grandfather was very well known and big businessman, wealthy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The guy, when was coming out from our apartment, he was going backwards and bowing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And now he became a big man, and he collaborated with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some of the people, the so-called [GERMAN], OD, they were also collaborating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not all of them, but they learned-- you know, this is a very known psychological fact.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You look up to somebody, and they were-- some of them were oppressing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I received many beatings, but the worst one was from the Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's alive some place in Australia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I should have-- if I would have been like I should have been, he would have hanged after the war in Poland, because I met him, and he deserved it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But then I didn't want to have blood on my hands.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But some of the [POLISH] behaved in German manner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were just-- I guess-- It's strange, but-- and very-- and very little is actually said about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And many of them, especially in Cracow, were killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They thought that they will survive, but they knew too much, as far as the German were concerned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they all died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that was-- Unfortunately, my mother's friend's husband, who was a doctor, he was doctor in our concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was also by Schindler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he came to Cracow after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the next day, he was put in prison and-- and he was hanged.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Many of them were hanged, and many run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
